{"image_id": "NVR_2017_page_52", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "NVR, Inc.", "bbox": [574.1, 25.1, 663.8, 48.1]}, {"text": "Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements", "bbox": [436.6, 50.1, 801.5, 73.1]}, {"text": "(dollars and shares in thousands, except per share data)", "bbox": [389.4, 75.1, 848.5, 98.1]}, {"text": "segment’s performance. The Company records charges on contract land deposits when it is determined that it is probable that recovery", "bbox": [56.3, 117.8, 1178.6, 140.9]}, {"text": "of the deposit is impaired. For segment reporting purposes, impairments on contract land deposits are charged to the operating", "bbox": [56.3, 142.8, 1113.6, 165.9]}, {"text": "segment upon the determination to terminate a Lot Purchase Agreement with the developer, or to restructure a Lot Purchase", "bbox": [56.3, 167.8, 1092.8, 190.9]}, {"text": "Agreement resulting in the forfeiture of the deposit. Mortgage banking profit before tax consists of revenues generated from mortgage", "bbox": [56.3, 192.8, 1178.6, 215.9]}, {"text": "financing, title insurance and closing services, less the costs of such services and general and administrative costs. Mortgage banking", "bbox": [56.3, 217.8, 1171.1, 240.9]}, {"text": "operations are not charged a corporate capital allocation charge.", "bbox": [56.3, 242.8, 589.4, 265.9]}, {"text": "In addition to the corporate capital allocation and contract land deposit impairments discussed above, the other reconciling", "bbox": [114.6, 280.3, 1136.5, 303.4]}, {"text": "items between segment profit and consolidated profit before tax include unallocated corporate overhead (including all management", "bbox": [56.3, 305.3, 1156.0, 328.4]}, {"text": "incentive compensation), equity-based compensation expense, consolidation adjustments and external corporate interest expense.", "bbox": [56.3, 330.4, 1139.5, 353.4]}, {"text": "NVR’s overhead functions, such as accounting, treasury and human resources are centrally performed and the costs are not allocated", "bbox": [56.3, 355.4, 1167.0, 378.4]}, {"text": "to the Company’s operating segments. Consolidation adjustments consist of such items necessary to convert the reportable segments’", "bbox": [56.3, 380.4, 1167.2, 403.4]}, {"text": "results, which are predominantly maintained on a cash basis, to a full accrual basis for external financial statement presentation", "bbox": [56.3, 405.4, 1121.9, 428.4]}, {"text": "purposes, and are not allocated to the Company’s operating segments. External corporate interest expense primarily consists of interest", "bbox": [56.3, 430.4, 1178.7, 453.5]}, {"text": "charges on the Company’s 3.95% Senior Notes due 2022 (the “Senior Notes”) and is not charged to the operating segments because", "bbox": [56.3, 455.4, 1160.7, 478.5]}, {"text": "the charges are included in the corporate capital allocation discussed above.", "bbox": [56.3, 480.4, 687.9, 503.5]}, {"text": "Following are tables presenting segment revenues, profit before taxes, assets, interest income, interest expense, depreciation", "bbox": [114.6, 517.9, 1149.2, 541.0]}, {"text": "and amortization and expenditures for property and equipment, with reconciliations to the amounts reported for the consolidated", "bbox": [56.3, 542.9, 1126.7, 566.0]}, {"text": "enterprise, where applicable:", "bbox": [56.3, 567.9, 296.5, 591.0]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [772.6, 624.3, 957.7, 642.8]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [704.5, 651.4, 737.8, 669.9]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [848.3, 651.4, 881.6, 669.9]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [992.1, 651.4, 1025.4, 669.9]}, {"text": "Revenues:", "bbox": [163.6, 678.1, 252.7, 701.1]}, {"text": "Homebuilding Mid Atlantic", "bbox": [188.6, 709.3, 420.7, 732.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [659.6, 709.3, 670.0, 732.4]}, {"text": "3,543,687", "bbox": [698.5, 709.3, 781.8, 732.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [803.4, 709.3, 813.8, 732.4]}, {"text": "3,319,776", "bbox": [842.3, 709.3, 925.6, 732.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [947.2,